 things. &quot;Anniversary&quot; seemed celebratory."}},{"is":"paragraph","props":{"text":"They considered going out of town but chose instead to stay and tried to pretend it was just another day."}},{"is":"paragraph","props":{"text":"Brittaney went to work, and Mollie kept herself busy trying to calculate where her son&apos;s name would fall in a chronological list of the 70,237 dead in 2017: Some 62,400 died before him and some 7,600 after. She thought if she could turn it into a math problem, maybe it might make some sense, but it didn&apos;t."}},{"is":"paragraph","props":{"text":"All day, Doug carted the box of Landon&apos;s ashes around with him. He sat it on his desk as he worked in his home office and put it in the passenger seat as he tooled around town running errands."}},{"is":"paragraph","props":{"text":"&quot;I hung out with Landon today,&quot; he told his family, before he put the box back on its shelf, in the living room, close by."}}],"short_urls":["https:\u002F\u002Ffxn.ws\u002F2G6lF6v"],"wp__category":{"title":"Health","slug":"health","path":"fox-news\u002Fhealth","isa_value":"health"},"fn__sections":[{"id":"b1ca9cb6-7b84-5465-91fb-c4f68e0a183d","path":"fox-news\u002Fhealth","isa_value":"health"}],"isAMP":false,"originalCanonical_url":"\u002Fhealth\u002Fi-couldnt-save-him-familys-pain-after-sons-overdose-death","header":{"headline":"'I couldn't save him': Family's pain after son's overdose death","subHeadline":"","authors":[],"source":{"name":"Associated Press","url":"http:\u002F\u002Fwww.ap.org\u002F"},"allowComments":true,"publicationDate":"2019-01-28T11:32:32-05:00","modifiedDate":"2019-01-28T11:32:39-05:00","lastPublishedDate":"2019-01-28T11:32:32-05:00","headerCategory":{"name":"Addiction","url":"\u002Fcategory\u002Fhealth\u002Fmental-health\u002Faddiction"},"category":{"name":"Health","url":"\u002Fhealth"},"organizationName":"Associated Press","organizationUrl":"http:\u002F\u002Fwww.ap.org\u002F"},"overlayType":"article"}},"ampCss":""},"Catego